title: LIVIN' it UP in LowerTown..Score in this1 br with private patio!

posting_body: ['Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a guided tour today!', 'CHOO!', 'CHOO!', "down to see what's goin' on in LowerTown!", ' Check outside your front door and patio.', 'Check out the fireworks after Friday nite Saints games!', 'See the colorful lights in the park as they sparkle with seasonal cheer!', ' Check out the friendly pubs and pizza pubs along the way--patio seating in the cool evening breezes.', 'This one bedroom, one bathroom apartment offers all day natural lighting, large main living space, walk-in closet and separated bedroom/entertaining areas.', ' Enjoy all new appliances!', 'Get a work out in using our 24/7 private Fitness Center and Studio, relax in our indoor heated pool and get toasty warm in our sauna.', 'Mears Park Place is owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Conveniently located in trendy Lowertown across from Mears Park, you can walk the skyway down to the river and bike along the Bike trails through the city parks.', 'We are just 2 blocks from Union Depot and the light rail station, which can take you through St. Paul and connects to Minneapolis and the University campus, as well as the airport.', ' Stop in at a friendly neighborhood pub--get a seat on the brightly lit patios--and enjoy the live music in the park.', 'Mears Park Place Apartments features:', '* Indoor Pool', '* Sun Patio', '*', 'Rec Room', '* Sauna', '* Tanning Bed', '* Party Room', '* 24hr gym with fitness studio', '* Underground Parking', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule your guided tour today!', '(Tell them you saw #B115 on Craigslist!)', '*Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
